column5: Looking for a quality outpost our group is 6-8 guys that are after quality Northern and Walleye wouldn't mind some lakers but not a must.

Try L+M flyins, I have used them 4 times in the past and plan to again this year. I have been to 3 different cabins and they were all very nice. We go with 6 guys and the walleye and northern fishing has always been awesome. I don't have there website address on hand, but you can just do a search for them and they'll come up.
